<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> ṣaḍasītyuttarē paruṣē saha
<lb n="2" break="no"/>srē ca śatōttarē <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kavivārē dhanurmmā sē kriṣṇa 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>vakṣē dvijōttamaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Āgatya ḍimilagrāmā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dvēmaṁgōḍāsthitōdhunā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīkūrmmanā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>thamāsādya jātatadbhaktiraṁjasā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> sūriśarmmē
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ti vikhyāta<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> svarnnamādhavasatsutaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yājña
<lb n="7" break="no"/>valkyō mahābuddhiḥ purataḥkamaṭhākṛtēḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="8"/>tāṁbrastaṁbbhēna sahitaṁ prādāddīpamakhaṁḍa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>kaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dharmmārtthaṁ kāmasiddhyartthaṁ yāvacchaṁ
<lb n="10" break="no"/>dradivākarau <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Evaṁ pradīpaṁ vurataḥ kū
<lb n="11" break="no"/>rmmanāthasya yē janāḥ pālayaṁti mahā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>puṇyaṁ tēṣāmastvaniśaṁ śubhaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīśrī
<lb n="13" break="no"/>śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

